      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 1.2333331228
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 2.5666665357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、息ピッタリで完璧だね！　芽衣もすずにゃんも\nお互い大好きだから、心も通じ合ってるのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3999999961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.8666678708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "は、恥ずかしげもなく言わないでくださいまし\nほら、休憩中にライブの衣装を決めますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2000011643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.3132437032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、候補の写真の中から、これだーって思ったのを\n指そうよ。いくよー、せーの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3132438303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.179910497
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.3999999881
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.7465752563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "お～、一緒のだ！　やっぱり通じ合ってるね～、あはは\n……？　うーん、そんなにじっと見つめないでほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4666660508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.2465727132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……み、見てないですわよっ！\n別に私は、芽衣と通じ合ってるだとかそんなこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2666635077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 52.0650076192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すずにゃんじゃなくて。うーん、苦手そうだし\nみんなのこと、あんまり言わない方がいいのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9650077463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.5983409525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私じゃない？　じゃあ、誰に言ったんですの……？\nうっ、また、なんだか気配がするような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.099996841,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4134.98922179999,
          "startTime": 65.7333301743
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9401.655888499996,
          "startTime": 70.999996841
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 72.0423995615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ひっ、おばあ様！？　び、びっくりしましたわ……\nでも安心しました。おばあ様の気配でしたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.899996841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 84.8865493418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あら、本日は頼み事で遅くまでお出掛けするんですのね\n心配御無用ですわ、芽衣のことは私がしっかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.199996841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 96.3865037562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　違う？　私が芽衣から離れるのが心配……？\nええ、と？　芽衣、今のは一体どういう意味……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6333301743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.9906537654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そこはねー……んー……秘密！　すずにゃん\n怖がりだから、夜、トイレ行けなくなっちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1906538925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.0573204321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "お手洗いぐらい、一人で行けますわっ！\nわ、私を子供扱いするんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0573204321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 127.3481402678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうつもりじゃなくって。苦手なものは誰でも――\nあ、言った傍から離れないでよ～、待って待って～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333340288,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4085.1937609999995,
          "startTime": 131.4333340288
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3499.999705999983,
          "startTime": 135.8333337348
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 132.3333340288
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 138.7241383197
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 138.7241383197
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 139.1000004014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "走り回ってなんとかまけましたわね……\n本当にずっと傍にいようとしてくるんですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5000004014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 148.575941845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ここで私が姿を消したらどんな反応をするのか\n気になりますわね。そうだ、この部屋に隠れて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4333337348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 160.8192281685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁっ！　はぁっ……！　すずにゃん、ダメっ！！\nその扉は開けないで！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0296668968,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 147.43686510001908,
          "startTime": 160.9666650336
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 167.5525615019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "わひゃっ、芽衣、いつの間に……！\nそれより、どうしてこの扉を開けちゃダメなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9666650336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 177.2992619796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、それも秘密なんだー\nすずにゃんがきっと聞きたくないことだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0992610894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 183.8659245772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、その……っ、今みたいにたまに聞こえる\nこの物音とは関係していますの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.0999831081,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fall-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2734.0585309000007,
          "startTime": 186.5999831081
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fall-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2734.0585309000007,
          "startTime": 186.5999831081
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 194.5200738234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、これは全然関係ないよ\nおじいちゃんが帰って来てるだけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
